<p>I'm trying to animate an Image when I send a request and then stop rotating that image when a response is received but I'm having trouble with the animation. </p>  <p>Here is what I have so far:</p>  <pre><code>    &lt;s:Sequence id="requestAnimation" repeatCount="0"&gt;         &lt;s:Parallel&gt;             &lt;s:Fade alphaFrom="1" alphaTo="0" target="{busyLogo}" duration="250" /&gt;             &lt;s:Fade alphaFrom="0" alphaTo="1" target="{cornerLogo}" duration="250" /&gt;         &lt;/s:Parallel&gt;         &lt;s:Sequence repeatCount="0"&gt;             &lt;s:Rotate3D angleZFrom="0"                          angleZTo="360"                          autoCenterProjection="true"                          autoCenterTransform="true"                          duration="1000"                         target="{busyLogo}" /&gt;         &lt;/s:Sequence&gt;     &lt;/s:Sequence&gt; </code></pre>  <p>The image rotates and when it gets to the end of a full rotation is slows to a stop and then starts up again. I would like it to rotate in one continuous loop. </p>